                  <formatted-text>
                    <run fontsize='11'>Early-warning screening dashboard for financially stressed firms based on liquidity, leverage, and earnings. </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#1f3a56' fontsize='12'>Key takeaway:</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#1f3a56' fontsize='12'> 2015 had the highest concentration of risky company-years, and CHTR was the only firm flagged in three separate years.</run>
